'''Abdalong of Marseilles''' was a bishop of the [[Diocese of Marseille]] in the 8th century<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/09715b.htm|title=CATHOLIC ENCYCLOPEDIA: Marseilles|work=newadvent.org}}</ref> during the reign of [[Charles Martel]]. He has a popular cult without official recognition which holds an informal [[feast day]] for him on March 1.

